title: 2020 NFL Divisional Power Rankings (Football 7/17)
description:
Will Brinson, Ryan Wilson and John Breech link up to rank all 8 NFL divisions. The guys follow Breech's list from CBSSports.com. While there wasn't a ton of agreement on this podcast, it was pretty clear that the NFC East and AFC East are the two worst divisions in football. From there, there isn't all that much separation. The Chiefs are the reigning Super Bowl champs, but how far can they carry the AFC West? The Bucs got Tom Brady...will that bolster the NFC South? The top division is another consensus, but we're not going to give that away here...
